text: Demange-Baudignécourt is a commune in the Meuse department in Grand Est in north-eastern France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Demange-aux-Eaux (the seat) and Baudignécourt.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Meuse department ==References== Category:Communes of Meuse (department) Category:Populated places established in 2019
title: Demange-Baudignécourt
